creator: Hungary Foundation
descriptionHtml:
MEET HuGo.

HuGo is the adventurous Hungarian hussar collecting all things Hungarian in the US. The uploads on his map are uploaded by the growing community of users, like you!

By building this community, HuGo's aim is to help everyone stay connected with Hungarian culture and people across America.

HuGo has a growing number of uploads uploaded by its users that are already available to explore! But there's more to be discovered - if you know of any locations or events that HuGo hasn’t marked yet - please ADD THEM to the map!
